data.description: LOWEST Priced Home In The Parkland's Newer Wedge Area!  3 Full Beds, 2.5 Baths Home w/Over $67K In Upgrades! Impact Windows & Doors, Gas Range, Spacious & Open Kitchen w/Quartz Counters, Stainless Steel Appliances, Ceramic Tile Throughout Main Living Areas, Wood Floors In All Beds, Private Fenced-In & Updated Landscaped Back Yard w/Room For Pool & Perfect For Children & Dogs. Under Cover Patio Area Ideal For Barbecues & Relaxing. Large Owner's Suite w/Sitting Area, Walk-In Closets w/Built-In's, Updated Primary Bath w/ Separate Tub & Huge 90 Degree Frameless Shower Enclosure, Updated Light Fixtures & Fans, Recently Epoxy Garage Floor, Resort-Style Amenities Including Clubhouse w/Heated Pool, Spa, Fitness Center, Tennis Courts, & More, 24-Hour Guard Gated, A-Rated Schools, & Low HOA Dues!
